<HEADLINE> Xinhua Home News Digest (at 23:30 Beijing Time, March 26) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
-- UN Secretary General to Visit China from March 31 to April 1
</P>
<P>
-- Tibet One of Most Concentrated Areas for Centenarians
