due to lack of direct links and we hope with this launch our
people will cease seeing each other as total strangers but as a
people who could do business together," she said.
</P>
<P>
She make the remarks during the inauguration of the airline's
services at Nairobi's Jomo Kenyatta International Airport
Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Jay Shanghavi, the local General Sales Agent for Alliance
Express, said the launch confirmed the carriers' dedication to
its goal of effectively connecting all countries in the Great
Lakes Region.
</P>
<P>
It would allow businessmen easy and quick access to the
Rwandese fast growing economy, he said.
</P>
<P>
Alliance Express which evolved after the demise of the
state-owned Air Rwanda in October last year is a joint venture
between the Rwandan government and the South Africa Airways.
</P>
<P>
It's an associate of Alliance Air which was set up in 1995 as
a joint venture between South African Airways, Uganda Airlines
and Air Tanzania. 
</P>
</TEXT>
